http://www.conservative.org:80/free/ST94/Downsizing94.html 204.71.237.88 19970208144350 text/html 7027
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 14:44:35 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:16:28 GMT
Content-length: 6842
