http://www.conservative.org:80/free/ST93/TrustFunds93.html 204.71.237.88 19970208144531 text/html 6564
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 14:46:16 GMT
