http://www.conservative.org:80/free/ST92/AlaskaWolf92.html 204.71.237.88 19970208145015 text/html 6626
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 14:51:00 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:08:23 GMT
Content-length: 6441
