<P><TT><B><A NAME="66">66</A></B></TT>  For a more
thorough explanation of  how Superfund should be reformed, see Shanahan, &quot;How
to Rescue Superfund: Bringing Common  Sense 
<!-- Generation of PM publication page 8 -->  to the Process.&quot; 
</P>
<P><TT><B><A NAME="67">67</A></B></TT>  Crandall and
Graham, &quot;New  FuelEconomy Standards.&quot;
</P>


