<P><TT><B><A NAME="22">22</A></B></TT>     Income groups refer to income 
quintiles. 
<!-- Generation of PM publication page 5 -->  That is, all families or
households are ranked top to bottom by income and divided into  fifths, creating
five income groups (bottom,  lower, middle, upper, and top).
