<P><A NAME="2"><b>2</b></A>     Article 1 of the GATT requires each  member to grant every other member treatment at least as favorable as it grants to its  most favored trading partner. Thus,  &quot;mostfavored&quot; is a misnomer. It actually refers to the normal trading status among nations. 
