http://www.conservative.org:80/mrc/medianomics/maywage.html 204.71.237.88 19970208150449 text/html 8387
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 15:05:33 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 22-Jul-96 18:21:46 GMT
