http://www.conservative.org:80/mrc/medianomics/febflat.html 204.71.237.88 19970208150159 text/html 9576
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 15:02:43 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 22-Jul-96 18:19:53 GMT
Content-length: 9391
