<TITLE>Directions to Fort Hunt Park</TITLE>
<BODY background="li-paper.gif TEXT="000000" LINK="0000FF" VLINK="FF0000" ALINK="93FF00">
<FONT SIZE=+2><BIG><STRONG><CENTER>Directions to Fort Hunt Park</CENTER></STRONG></BIG></FONT>
<HR>

<HEAD>
<FONT SIZE=+1><BIG>Beltway from Virginia:</BIG></FONT>
</HEAD>

<BODY>
<p>From 95N take exit 1 North.
Go to the first traffic light.
Take a right on Franklin St.
Go about three blocks  take a right on  S.
Washington Street.
Continue 5 miles exit "Fort Hunt/Fort Hunt Picnic Area."<p>
</BODY>
<HR>
<HEAD>
<FONT SIZE=+1><BIG>Beltway from Maryland:</BIG></FONT>
</HEAD>

  <BODY>
<p>From the Wilson Bridge take  first exit (Mt. Venon Hwy.).
This will put you on South Washington Street.
Continue 5 miles exit "Fort Hunt/Fort Hunt  Picnic Area."<p>
</BODY>
 <HR>
<HEAD>
<FONT SIZE=+1><BIG>From DC: </BIG></FONT>
</HEAD>

<BODY>
<p>Take 14th Street Bridge. Go South on George
Washington Memorial Parkway. Go 5 miles South of Alexandria.
Take exit "Fort Hunt Rd/Fort Hunt Picnic Area."<p>
</BODY>
