<H2><FONT SIZE=+3>T</FONT>he  <FONT SIZE=+3>H</FONT>eritage <FONT SIZE=+3>F</FONT>oundation</H2>
    
<h3>Featured Chart for the week of February 3, 1997</h3>

<p>
<b>Some Federally Required Burdens on Workers</b>

<img src="/heritage/library/categories/regulation/fyi129t1.gif" width=426 height=533 border=0 alt=" Some Federally Required Burdens on Workers">
</center><p>

 <font size="-1">Graphic by Thomas J. Timmons
<p>
Source: <a href="/heritage/library/categories/regulation/fyi129.html"> Senator Abraham's Mandates Information Act: The Way To Help Congress Work Smarter</a> by Angela Antonelli and Mark Wilson. Heritage <i>F.Y.I.</I> No. 129, February 6, 1997.

